{
  "stem": "21817.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They were afraid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Because at night, another group would come and burn the house down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "The partisan would do it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "There were lots of partisans in the woods over there, many groups.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "They were not yet under one command.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "They were still not organized.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And-- and that's the way we started living a little bit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And right away, I used to eat like a, like a horse.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Everybody get one bowl of soup.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I used to have three or four.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I was, I was so hungry from such a long time not eating.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And suddenly, I put on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "I became a regular man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And then we started off to get organized.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And from little to little-- we used to shoot up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "Used to-- everything was done at night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "At day time, we were in the camp, the patrols outside see if no Germans come in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "In 1943 already, the partisan were very strong already.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "The-- some of the, of the partisans had already-- there were regular Russian troops, which they did not surrender to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "They got contact with the, I assume, Russian Army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And they used to, with airplanes, throw down guns and ammunition, paratroopers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "There were some paratroopers already over there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And they start to organize the whole area.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "Well, still, I mean, they stayed away from us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "Because they know it's a family camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But we wanted to fight ourselves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And I joined one, one of those fighting groups.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And we used to do explosive things with the trains that used to go over there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "Once, I was selected with four more men.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And we didn't know how to use dynamite.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So we were carrying the, the dynamite on our backs and find a spot in the wood.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
